{"tid":101672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州地鐵男子打老人：沒有我們納稅，你哪有錢養老","createTime":"2017-01-31T05:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T11:03:33.000Z","uid":41375,"like":82,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf4e11b5bcdf4d6244bce9901cde1450b455aea","tid":101672,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.weibo.cn/status/4066994460604566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fstatus%2F4066994460604566&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo50%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=42301790\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.weibo.cn/status/4066994460604566</a><br />\n【男子地鐵打老人：沒有我們納稅，你哪有錢養老】1月17日早上，廣州地鐵8號線，一名年輕人和鄰座老伯發生衝突。老伯稱，男子嫌孩子碰到他的手臂，就用手肘撞了他的孫子，於是二人發生爭吵，後演變為肢體衝突。眾人勸架，但男子仍然不罷休，老伯多處受傷。 （廣東電視台）<br />\n<br />\n片:<a href=\"http://m.miaopai.com/show/channel/FeK19Kd~3vFIz4kAsjjomw__\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.miaopai.com%2Fshow%2Fchannel%2FFeK19Kd~3vFIz4kAsjjomw__&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo50%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3846dd38\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.miaopai.com/show/channel/FeK19Kd~3vFIz4kAsjjomw__</a>"},{"pid":"b0211963080243990b2ea64f99d560bdad59a240","tid":101672,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"打得好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過最好連個後生仔都俾人槍斃，因為支那人冇一個係無辜嘅！"},{"pid":"e54a351464a3e397459b04b14dd58ec60c265487","tid":101672,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"da56a43685bbb193a7bf14dbdccdc6e0396fb8fd","tid":101672,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"真理"},{"pid":"b2d6cabf5a3cb49fbc95fc80dbaaf96bd429f099","tid":101672,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"英雄"},{"pid":"a0d78c82a84fb2072ee6586274948a6fefb8493f","tid":101672,"uid":84,"like":0,"dislik